      "text": "Some Root Metaphors pass the [[Criteria for Adequacy for a Hypothesis]].  Others do not pass.\n\n* Four [[Relatively Adequate World Hypotheses]] were published by Pepper in 1942.\n\n* Two [[Inadequate World Hypotheses]] were published in 1942.\n\n* Additional [[Proposed World Hypothesis]] have been surfaced by Pepper, and by other researchers, but have not yet undergone rigourous review."
